title: High Winds Knock Out SMUD Power For Arden, Carmichael Residents

organizations.name: smud power for arden, carmichael residents sacramento

text:
SACRAMENTO (CBS13) — High winds from a strong storm have knocked out power to nearly 20,000 SMUD customers on Tuesday.
SMUD’s outage map has most of the outages concentrated in the Arden area, with more than 17,000 without power.
Next is Carmichael with nearly 1,300 out.
Trees down all over Sacramento, heavy rain & high winds the culprit! Check out this one in South Sac neighborhood @CBSSacramento Live at 10! pic.twitter.com/PqC7ze6lcW 
— JENN MCGRAW CBS13 (@NewsMcGraw) January 4, 2017 

Estimated time for restoration is somewhere before midnight.
